      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;./Wind-River-AWS-Automotive.webp&#34; alt=&#34;Wind River and AWS collaborate to Advance SDA Innovation&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description>
